{
  "stem": "5328.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "So he-- they said, if you-- we find a Jew hidden in our place, in any place, so you'll be shot and the Jew will be shot.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "So they were afraid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I would do the same thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "I would be afraid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, no, they wouldn't let-- let me stay.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, but they wouldn't let me stay.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They said, here's a piece of bread and-- and-- and bacon and-- and clothes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But go.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I ate the bacon later on, but I couldn't-- [LAUGHS] I couldn't in the moment.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After I had to leave the farm-- see, [INAUDIBLE] was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That means that the railroad had to be changed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Russian railroad was narrow and the Polish railroads wider.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was one particular spot that is they had to change from narrow to wide, from-- from Russia to Polish.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I knew exactly where that particular spot-- so every-- every-- this transport that came from Russia had to stop and change the-- the railroad and go further.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they were taking-- the-- the Germans were taking the youth, the-- the-- the Russian youth, Polish too.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that time come from Russia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They took the youth to work in Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because all their younger generations were on the-- on the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they had to do-- produce in-- in Germany too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had the farmers and the factories to work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they had to have people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they brought the young generation from-- from Russia and brought it into Germany.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I knew that spot where they changed the railroad.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I came to that spot, and it exactly stayed a-- a transfer with about 2,000 people, young-- young people, that were transferred to Germany.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I came up to that German, and I start crying.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
